reviewText: Do you hate your life because you go through the day-to-day struggling just to make a single dollar and you seem to never get anywhere in life because it seems like everything that you want just Slips Away by the slip of a straw well look no farther for a show that can closely relate to your living situation this witty Show gives a wide variety of almost correct sequences of the World War II Nazi propaganda with a American Australian twist to it this show is everything I've ever dreamed of in a shell from rude commentary to obscene creatures I wish I could give this show more than five stars I wish I could give it my soul
